snippet.title: X018- Sea of Thieves The Arena Announce
snippet.description:
As announced at X018, The Arena is the latest content update from Sea of Thieves. Prove your worth to the Sea Dogs as you battle to the top of The Arena in an all new PVP based mode coming to the Sea of Thieves in Early 2019! Get Xbox Game Pass: https://www.xbox.com/xbox-game-pass

Learn more about Sea of Thieves or Buy Now: www.xbox.com/seaofthieves
